Specifications:
STRUCTURE : Ground + 1 floor - RCC framed structure with 6"" solid block masonry.&nbsp;
MAIN DOOR: 7' height door with WPC/equivalent frame and both side masonite skin shutters.&nbsp;
INTERNAL DOORS: WPC/Equivalent door frames with design moulded skin shutter.&nbsp;
WINDOWS : Three track heavy duty UPVC sliding windows with mosquito mesh and MS grill.&nbsp;
FLOORING : Superior quality 80x80 vitrified tile flooring in living/dining, bed rooms &amp; kitchen. Ceramic tile flooring in bathrooms.&nbsp;
KITCHEN : 20mm granite platform with stainless steel sink with drain board in kitchen.&nbsp;
CP FITTINGS : Jaquar/Kohler/equivalent for bathrooms &amp; kitchen.&nbsp;
SANITARY FITTING : White Kohler or equivalent sanitary wares.&nbsp;
ELECTRICAL &amp; WIRING : Concealed wiring with premium quality ISI brand PVC conduits &amp; Finolex / Havells or equivalent wires for lighting and heating circuits.&nbsp;
SWITCHES : Anchor/Lagrand/Roma or equivalent modular switches. TV points in living and master bed room. Telephone points in living and master bed room.&nbsp;
PAINTING : Internal: Two coats of emulsion paint - roller finish forwalls &amp; ceiling External: Two coats of emulsion sponge finish over a coat of primer.&nbsp;
POWER BACKUP : Invertors will be provided - batteries to be purchased by clients. Note : All materials stated above are subject to availability.
